data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION !! Bring your best offer. Assumable loan! Seller Motivated! Make your offer today. Welcome to Saint Cloud !!Price Includes alkaline and water softener system and solar panels. This spacious property has ample space for your whole family. This open floor concept has a bright Kitchen which is the heart of the home for gatherings and entertainment, great dinning area, a down stairs study room, great living space and a half bathroom. The second floor provides the master room, master bathroom, two rooms and another bathroom. Also has a great loft and the laundry room is very spacious with extra closet space. This extended lot has a fenced in backyard, more than 12 feet from each property, solar panels, and water softener system. This can be your chance to call this property home and able to enjoy the Saint Cloud life style. Surrounded  with great food, golf courses, different grocery stores, 5 minutes from the turnpike, 30 minutes from theme parks, and 25 minutes from the Lake Nona area.
